org.jbones.schedule

Class TaskWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.TimerTask
      • org.jbones.schedule.TaskWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable

    public class TaskWrapper
extends java.util.TimerTask
implements java.io.Serializable
    a wrapper around a java task that contains functionality to track the state and other statistics of the task. the state can be one of INITIALIZED, IDLE, RUNNING, CANCELING, CANCELED, FAILED.
